SELECT `station` AS `station_e8ed3f`, `time` AS `time_07cc69`, `NO2` AS `NO2_91b760`, `O3` AS `O3_9ee25e`, `H2S` AS `H2S_8f5dce`, `CO` AS `CO_42983b`, `SO2` AS `SO2_260405`, `Температура, °С` AS `Температура, °С_ed821f`, `davlenie` AS `davlenie_53f2c3`, `vlazhnost` AS `vlazhnost_2442c8`, `Скорость ветра, м/с` AS `Скорость ветра, м/с_42ba1e`, `Направление ветра, °` AS `Направление ветра, °_20a590` 
FROM (SELECT
    sd.station,
    _t.timeStamp AS time,
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.pollutant_name = 'NO₂' THEN _t.value END) AS NO2,
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.pollutant_name = 'O₃' THEN _t.value END) AS O3,
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.pollutant_name = 'H₂S' THEN _t.value END) AS H2S,
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.pollutant_name = 'CO' THEN _t.value END) AS CO,
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.pollutant_name = 'SO₂' THEN _t.value END) AS SO2,
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.microclimate_param_name = 'Температура' THEN _t.value END) AS "Температура, °С",
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.microclimate_param_name = 'Давление' THEN _t.value END) AS davlenie,
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.microclimate_param_name = 'Влажность' THEN _t.value END) AS vlazhnost,
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.microclimate_param_name = 'Скорость ветра' THEN _t.value END) AS "Скорость ветра, м/с",
    MAX(CASE WHEN sd.microclimate_param_name = 'Направление ветра' THEN _t.value END) AS "Направление ветра, °"
FROM
    pg_vw_analytics_dashboard.combined_sensor_data sd
JOIN 
    trend.trends _t ON _t.idTrend = sd.trend_id
WHERE
    sd.domain_id = 'a530c185-65ef-4841-9e93-4dfa05550605'
GROUP BY
    sd.station,
    _t.timeStamp
ORDER BY
    sd.station DESC,
    _t.timeStamp ASC
) AS `virtual_table` 
WHERE `time` >= toDateTime('2025-05-14 00:00:00') AND `time` < toDateTime('2025-05-21 00:00:00')
 LIMIT 50000;
